<dl id="n12018g"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12018g">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12018g"> 18(g)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> if &amp; belladonna poison</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Quand le flambeau avait disparu, elle vidait une coupe remplie du suc empoisonn&eacute; de l&apos;if m&ecirc;l&eacute; de belladone. Aussit&ocirc;t un sommeil lourd engourdissait ses membres, et d&apos;&eacute;paisses t&eacute;n&egrave;bres recouvraient pour toujours les yeux de la voyante. <br><font color="green">[When the torch had disappeared, she emptied a cup filled with poisoned juice of taxus mixed with belladonna. Immediately a deep sleep came over his limbs and thick shadows covered forever the eyes of the seer.]</font> <small> &Eacute;douard Schur&eacute;, <a name="ESLL" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#ESLL"><cite title="source">Les Grandes L&eacute;gendes de France</cite></a> (1892) 153</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
